{"tid":246852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（絲打入）我ex好似廢柴令我唔想再拍拖","createTime":"2017-05-17T10:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T14:16:21.000Z","uid":107294,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06b8d246e1e69b53ebcd71e89e7614d67d8c7c20","tid":246852,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T10:46:26.000Z","msg":"一個女仔係想被照顧 <br />\n但反而一個男仔需要我照顧<br />\n仲大條道理 咩事都指意你 <br />\n：你安排啦 隨便啦 是旦啦 我都唔知 我都唔識 點行呀<br />\n聽厭條廢柴講野 真係時候一刀兩斷<br />\n當然仲有好多問題 <br />\n<br />\n我知ex睇到 但我講依堆野唔係想同ex復合<br />\n我想講同完廢柴分手 我感到前所未有既自由<br />\n我唔再做男朋友阿媽 ！<br />\n不過都多謝佢令我明白女仔真係唔好為想拍拖而拖<br />\n真係要拍拖前知佢既問題 知佢既缺點<br />\n我就係一切來得太快 <br />\n依家我真係未有最好都唔會拍 一定不比佢差先<br />\n<br />\n有無絲打有同感？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f7ebad971d5215e15d74cef72eecbe82328b16","tid":246852,"uid":81686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"中學？"},{"pid":"6f1305668a89c4f6e9063fa4f48e8b629c9e3441","tid":246852,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T10:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學？</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"07fbf72cba53ec3bd7982df1cd5b9095440edf90","tid":246852,"uid":81686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中學？</blockquote><br />\n係</blockquote><br />\n唔好搵中學既拖"},{"pid":"b5fe03dcbfc7bd349a1d066e2e878de78ef56416","tid":246852,"uid":6860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:00:43.000Z","msg":"中學應該係你最開心既時候，因為你地係唔會因為物質去拍拖，但都可以搞成咁"},{"pid":"96444e4f466150f9abfde764d9ec47c3428d38b2","tid":246852,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中學？</blockquote><br />\n係</blockquote><br />\n唔好搵中學既拖</blockquote><br />\n中學拍拖係經歷"},{"pid":"e250453267e87a2e57c9de16504529d4b82f815f","tid":246852,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r